casebody.data:
Teddy GARCIA, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
The STATE of Florida, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D18-0553, 3D18-0432 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. October 4, 2018 ROTHENBERG, C.J., and SALTER and LINDSEY, JJ., concur.

Upon the Court's own motion, it is ordered that these consolidated appeals from the Circuit Court for Miami-Dade County, Florida are dismissed for failure to comply with this Court's order dated September 4, 2018, and with the Florida Rules of Appellate Procedure.
